; GUID_TFCAT_DISPLAYATTRIBUTEPROVIDER -- exposes GUID_DISPLAYATTR_INPUT to
; Windows so Composition.cpp's GUID_PROP_ATTRIBUTE property gets honoured
; when painting the preedit range (dotted blue underline).
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\CTF\TIP\{CADA0001-1234-5678-90AB-CDEF00000001}\Category\Category\{13A016DF-560B-46CD-947A-4C3AF1E0E35D}]
